title: Impressive Rookie Quarterbacks With Bucky Brooks and Trades to Look Out For | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Kevin is joined by NFL Network‘s Bucky Brooks to discuss which rookie quarterback will be first to compete in the AFC, how the Cowboys can turn it around, and how the Pittsburgh Steelers keep drafting good wide receivers. Then Kevin is joined by The Ringer’s Nora Princiotti, Danny Kelly, and Kaelen Jones to discuss three trades that they each want to see.
Host: Kevin Clark 
Guest: Bucky Brooks, Nora Princiotti, Danny Kelly, and Kaelen Jones
